Package adris.altoclef

Class StaticMixinHookups

java.lang.Object
adris.altoclef.StaticMixinHookups
public class StaticMixinHookups extends Object
Connects client mixins to our AltoClef instance Mixins have no way (currently) to access our mod.

As a result I'll do this statically.

However, I want to avoid grabbing AltoClef in a static context, so this class serves at the "static dumpster" which is the only spot where I allow the bad practice of singletons to flourish
